This middle-aged man has the confidence of winning many battles, and the strength to back that up.

Forged by the fire giant Varboti as a gift for a Cormyrian general who made peace with his clan, this red-and-black armor lends its wearer a molten aspect while providing protection against almost all but the most powerful blows. Due to its incredibly strong thin material, it also weighs far less than ordinary plate mail.
This robe sends shivers all over your skin when you touch it.  Its many colors reflect the types of energy it absorbs.

Judging by his uniform and colors, this man appears to be a soldier from Luskan. The demeanor and attitude of their soldiers has lead many to mistake them for bandits, and more often not it is not far from the truth.
